						               													<description>Get Ready... get steady... and try not to get wreckt! In Battle for the Hill, players collect points in a fast-paced futuristic race of sports stars with amazing abilities. Use action cards to slow down other players or join together and K.O. the many obstacles standing in your way. Stuck? Players can reprogram &amp;ldquo;cobot&amp;rdquo; referees, who are standing by on the sidelines waiting to help them out.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;What&amp;rsquo;s a cobot?&amp;#10;A cobot, short for &amp;ldquo;collaborative robot&amp;rdquo;, is a robot that helps people and works alongside them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game includes four sports-themed card suits: Boxing, Football, Basketball, and Weightlifting. A fifth cobot-themed suit allows players to affect the different sections of The Hill, boosting their performance. On your turn, you can play one (or sometimes more!) cards to move your team up The Hill, slow down your opponents, OR change the cobot programming to give you a strategic advantage. So, bring your A game, and try not to get sacked!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
